<name>PRECAUTION</name>
<subpara id="RM000000PD800NX_z0" proc-id="RM0250U___000078O00000">
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<atten3>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Perform RESET MEMORY (AT initialization) when replacing the automatic transmission assembly, engine assembly or ECM (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000W7F01YX"/>).</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Perform REGISTRATION (VIN registration) when replacing the ECM (See page <xref label="Seep02" href="RM000000PDT013X"/>).</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten3>
<atten4>
<ptxt>Initialization cannot be completed by removing the battery.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</content5>
</subpara>
